-- Philippine President Aquino on Economy, Mining Policy
-- B y
-- 2012-05-07T03:00:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-07/philippine-president-aquino-on-economy-mining-policy-video-.html
Philippine President  Benigno Aquino  
speaks about the nation's economy, relations with China on 
territorial claims over oil and gas resources, and the nation's 
mining policy.  Aquino said the Philippine economy likely grew at least 5.2
percent in the first quarter, the fastest pace in more than a 
year. He also discussed the nation's currency with Bloomberg's 
Christopher Anstey, Clarissa Batino and Joel Guinto in Manila on
May 4. (Source: Bloomberg)  00:00 Economic growth expectations; China relations
02:34 Mining policy; outlook for the peso  Running time 04:39
 